  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses foods available at a public school.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>exempts foods made available for distribution from a school-based food pantry (pantry), including a teen center, from lawful presence verification requirements for receipt of a food item from the pantry; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
